      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Welcome back to The Long View. I'm joined by Skanda Amarnath, who reads the macroeconomy for a living. Skanda, good to have you."
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:e561fff4c04db8b9",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "You describe macro as risk management. Unpack that."
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:646137f8417f698c",
      "properties": {
        "confidence": 0.7,
        "grounded": true,
        "text": "Macro is risk management at scale. The job is mostly not being on the wrong side of a regime change \u2014 and the regime change you can name in advance is the one you can position for. The rest is just\u2026"
      },
      "type": "Insight"
    },
    {
